Vulois

Vulois looked at the group.

"Yeah, that's fine. Sky Schorchers.I like it. Down the hallway their 
are a whole bunch of rooms. They are quarters. The far three are 
booked, with me, Battera, and Soundwave's old which I guess will be 
Cybershark's now. You gouy can take some. I don't know if theirs 
enough, you may have to doulbe up or something. Leave on for Child, 
he'll need privacy."

Vulois turned back to Child.
______________________________________________________________________
Starscream

Starscream, carrying Reptillica, arrived at the Alliance base. He 
stopped infront of the door.

"Take me to Zardus."
______________________________________________________________________
Trainers/Savage

The Trainers walked out of their base, with Prebon riding on Savage's 
back. Savage was constantly angry at at The Trainers, that is why he 
is in dragon mode, but the chip inside him prohibits him from 
actually doing damae to him. Prebon yelld out to the others.

"Blaze! Do you have the co-ordinates for The Ark?"

"Yes I do sir."

"Good. Everyone follow Blaze. Now we start our war!"

The Trainers and Savage marched on to the Ark.
